    Dad's pre-existing condition disqualifies SafetyWing Nomad immediately. Cigna can underwrite the blood pressure and likely cover it (with possible exclusion initially). The kids get full pediatric care. Routine checkups are covered. Direct billing means no out-of-pocket hassles with four people needing care.
  </p>

